                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#ir(ecto) #iv(erso)" facs="001 002"/><desc>Crude drawings of several figures, some in pencil and some in blue ink</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#iir(ecto)" facs="002"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1082Angel"/> with <term key="sword"/> and <term key="scabbard"/>, with seven talismanic faces to the left in boxes</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#iiv(erso)" facs="003"/><desc>An Ethiopian dignitary (left), holds a large ornate <ref type ="authFile" corresp="AT1071Cross"/>. Another man (right), holds a rifle by the barrel with a hand cross behind him. Above both are two figures, one holding an umbrella for the other and a church in the center background with captions (l. to r.) <q>“Jesus’ Cross,”</q> <q>“The Ark,”</q> <q>“Processional Umbrella (Dǝbab),”</q> <q>“Saviour of the World,”</q> and <q>“rifle.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4"><locus target="#87r" facs="089"/><desc>King Herod supervising the scourging of <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1084JesusChrist"/> with captions <q>“King Herod,”</q> <q>“Our Lord scourced,”</q> <q>“Jews,”</q> and <q>“Jews.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d5"><locus target="#88v" facs="091"/>An <desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1082Angel"/> with <term key="sword"/> and <term key="scabbard"/>, in black ink</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d6"><locus target="#89r" facs="091"/><desc>Two <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1082Angel"/>s with <term key="sword"/>s and <term key="scabbard"/>s, in pencil</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d7"><locus target="#89v" facs="092"/><desc>Crude drawings of two figures and a bird</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d8"><locus target="#Back inside cover" facs="092"/><desc>Crude drawing of two men</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d9">
